<help communications describe>

Allows you to modify your description.  This is the possibly
long description that someone sees when they look at you.
You may enter up to 10 lines, each line must be no longer than
80 characters, or it will be automatically wrapped.  You may
change your description as often as you like.

Syntax:  describe

Example:  describe

<color=red>
See Also:  title
</color></help>
